# Power BI Sales Analysis Dashboard

## Project Overview
This project presents a sales analysis dashboard built using Power BI.  
The dashboard analyzes sales performance, profit, and product categories using the SuperStore dataset.

## Dataset
SuperStoreOrders.csv

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Power BI
- Power BI Fabric
- Data Modeling
- DAX
- Row Level Security (RLS)

## Features
- Sales analysis by year
- Sales by category
- Total profit KPI
- Interactive filters
- Role Level Security (RLS)

